<p>I want that camera follow the player. For this I use player's(in target) transform and change camera's transform.  </p>  <pre><code>public class CameraScript : MonoBehaviour {     public Transform target;     private Vector3 delta;      void Start()     {         delta = Camera.main.transform.position - target.position;     }      void Update()     {         Camera.main.transform.position = target.position + delta;     } } </code></pre>  <p>This method works, but it's a better solution?</p>